<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
gossip [message] : send [message] to the global gossip chat channel<br>
gossip [on|off]  : turn gossip on or off<br>
gossip           : displays last ten gossips<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
Use this channel for talking about mud related topics in character. <br>
Use of this channel also requires gossip points.  It costs ten gossip<br>
points to gossip once.  The points accumulate over time, and unuse of the<br>
gossip channel.  To see how many gossip points your character has<br>
accumulated, type "score" (see help score); the points are listed<br>
under Gsp_points . <br>
<br>
See also: help channels<br>
